    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3144070/extras/48cb43d274c05f2fbee8322ff166827f.webp?t=1761586444\" width=601 height=33 /></span><br><strong>CINEMA</strong> is an immersive <strong>thriller</strong> adventure game where the player wields <strong>control over time</strong> and the intricate interplay of cause and effect within an environment inspired by <strong>silent films</strong>. With the ability to navigate diverse <strong>timelines</strong> and even create entirely new ones, the player experiences a unique and captivating gameplay mechanic.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3144070/extras/d68efc2820cbd6f5f1dbda11c0ccb6cf.webp?t=1761586444\" width=601 height=33 /></span><br>Interact with mysterious characters while gathering crucial clues and evidence to solve the case.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3144070/extras/7f56c06b734e53948ea4a744fd2a8633.poster.avif?t=1761586444\" width=600 height=190 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3144070/extras/7f56c06b734e53948ea4a744fd2a8633.webm?t=1761586444\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3144070/extras/7f56c06b734e53948ea4a744fd2a8633.mp4?t=1761586444\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3144070/extras/e171d0a648ab4cebcaea9c1412d24903.webp?t=1761586444\" width=601 height=33 /></span><br>Navigate through time by moving both forward and backward, and explore rich Art Deco environments across space and moments in time.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"